                <div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
                    <p>An Accounting Operation Management System (Accounting System) is a structure that a business uses to collect, store, manage, process, retrieve and report its financial data so that it can be used by accountants, consultants, business analysts, managers, chief financial officers (CFOs), auditors, regulators&nbsp;and tax agencies.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
                <div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-1" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block">
